quran[149]{c,v,t}:
  5,82,LETEXHIDENNE ‘ESHEDDE EN-NASI ‘ADAWETEN LILLEDHINE ‘AMENUL-JEHUDE WEL-LEDHINE ‘ESHREKU WE LETEXHIDENNE ‘EKREBEHUM MEWEDDETEN LILLEDHINE ‘AMENUL-LEDHINE KALU ‘INNA NESARA DHALIKE BI’ENNE MINHUM KISSISINE WE RUHBANÆN WE ‘ENNEHUM LA JESTEKBIRUNE
  5,83,WE ‘IDHA SEMI’U MA ‘UNZILE ‘ILA ER-RESULI TERA ‘A’JUNEHUM TEFIDU MINE ED-DEM’I MIMMA ‘AREFU MINEL-HEKKI JEKULUNE REBBENA ‘AMENNA FAKTUBNA ME’A ESH-SHAHIDINE
  5,84,WE MA LENA LA NU’UMINU BILLAHI WE MA XHA’ENA MINEL-HEKKI WE NETMA’U ‘EN JUDHILENA REBBUNA ME’AL-KAWMI ES-SALIHINE
  5,85,FE’ETHABEHUMU ELLAHU BIMA KALU XHENNATIN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU HALIDINE FIHA WE DHELIKE XHEZA’UL-MUHSININE
  5,86,WEL-LEDHINE KEFERU WE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA ‘ULA’IKE ‘ESHABUL-XHEHIMI
  5,87,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TUHERRIMU TEJJIBATI MA ‘EHELLEL-LAHU LEKUM WE LA TA’TEDU ‘INNALL-LLAHE LA JUHIBBUL-MU’TEDINE
  5,88,WE KULU MIMMA REZEKAKUMU ELLAHU HELALÆN TEJJIBÆN WE ETTEKU ELLAHEL-LEDHI ‘ENTUM BIHI MU’UMINUNE
  5,89,LA JU’UAHIDHUKUMU ELLAHU BIL-LEGWI FI ‘EJMANIKUM WE LEKIN JU’UAHIDHUKUM BIMA ‘AKKADTUMUL-’IMANE FEKEFFARETUHU ‘IT’AMU ‘ASHERETI MESAKINE MIN ‘EWSETI MA TUT’IMUNE ‘EHLIKUM ‘EW KISWETUHUM ‘EW TEHRIRU REKABETIN FEMEN LEM JEXHID FESIJAMU THELATHETI ‘EJJAMIN D
  5,90,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘INNEMAL-HAMRU WEL-MEJSIRU WEL-’ENSABU WEL-’EZLAMU RIXHSUN MIN ‘AMELI ESH-SHEJTANI FAXHTENIBUHU LE’ALLEKUM TUFLIHUNE
  5,91,‘INNEMA JURIDU ESH-SHEJTANU ‘EN JUKI’A BEJNEKUMUL-’ADAWETE WEL-BEGDA’E FIL-HAMRI WEL-MEJSIRI WE JESUDDEKUM ‘AN DHIKRI ELLAHI WE ‘ANI ES-SELÆTI FEHEL ‘ENTUM MUNTEHUNE
  5,92,WE ‘ETI’U ELLAHE WE ‘ETI’U ER-RESULE WE EHDHERU FE’IN TEWELLEJTUM FA’LEMU ‘ENNEMA ‘ALA RESULINAL-BELAGUL-MUBINU
  5,93,LEJSE ‘ALEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI XHUNAHUN FIMA TA’IMU ‘IDHA MA ETTEKAW WE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI THUMME ETTEKAW WE ‘AMENU THUMME ETTEKAW WE ‘EHSENU WEL-LAHU JUHIBBUL-MUHSININE
  5,94,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LEJEBLUWENNEKUMU ELLAHU BISHEJ’IN MINE ES-SEJDI TENALUHU ‘EJDIKUM WE RIMAHUKUM LIJA’LEMEL-LAHU MEN JEHAFUHU BIL-GAJBI FEMENI A’TEDA BA’DE DHALIKE FELEHU ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  5,95,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TEKTULU ES-SEJDE WE ‘ENTUM HURUMUN WE MEN KATELEHU MINKUM MUTE’AMMIDÆN FEXHEZA’UN MITHLU MA KATELE MINE EN-NE’AMI JEHKUMU BIHI DHEWA ‘ADLIN MINKUM HEDJÆN BALIGAL-KA’BETI ‘EW KEFFARETUN TA’AMU MESAKINE ‘EW ‘ADLU DHALIKE SIJAMÆ
  5,96,‘UHILLE LEKUM SEJDUL-BEHRI WE TA’AMUHU META’ÆN LEKUM WE LILSSEJJARETI WE HURRIME ‘ALEJKUM SEJDUL-BERRI MA DUMTUM HURUMÆN WE ETTEKU ELLAHEL-LEDHI ‘ILEJHI TUHSHERUNE
  5,97,XHE’ALEL-LAHUL-KA’BETEL-BEJTEL-HERAME KIJAMÆN LILNNASI WE ESH-SHEHREL-HERAME WEL-HEDJE WEL-KALA’IDE DHALIKE LITA’LEMU ‘ENNEL-LAHE JA’LEMU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE BIKULLI SHEJ’IN ‘ALIMUN
  5,98,A’LEMU ‘ENNEL-LAHE SHEDIDUL-’IKABI WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE GAFURUN REHIMUN
  5,99,MA ‘ALA ER-RESULI ‘ILLAL-BELAGU WEL-LAHU JA’LEMU MA TUBDUNE WE MA TEKTUMUNE
  5,100,KUL LA JESTEWIL-HABITHU WET-TEJJIBU WE LEW ‘A’XHEBEKE KETHRETUL-HABITHI FE ETTEKU ELLAHE JA ‘ULIL-’ELBABI LE’ALLEKUM TUFLIHUNE
  5,101,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TES’ELU ‘AN ‘ESHJA’E ‘IN TUBDE LEKUM TESU’UKUM WE ‘IN TES’ELU ‘ANHA HINE JUNEZZELUL-KUR’ANU TUBDE LEKUM ‘AFALLAHU ‘ANHA WEL-LAHU GAFURUN HELIMUN
  5,102,KAD SE’ELEHA KAWMUN MIN KABLIKUM THUMME ‘ESBEHU BIHA KAFIRINE
  5,103,MA XHE’ALEL-LAHU MIN BEHIRETIN WE LA SA’IBETIN WE LA WESILETIN WE LA HAMIN WE LEKINNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU JEFTERUNE ‘ALA ELLAHIL-KEDHIBE WE ‘EKTHERUHUM LA JA’KILUNE
  5,104,WE ‘IDHA KILE LEHUM TA’ALEW ‘ILA MA ‘ENZELEL-LAHU WE ‘ILA ER-RESULI KALU HESBUNA MA WEXHEDNA ‘ALEJHI ‘ABA’ENA ‘EWELEW KANE ‘ABA’UUHUM LA JA’LEMUNE SHEJ’ÆN WE LA JEHTEDUNE
  5,105,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘ALEJKUM ‘ENFUSEKUM LA JEDURRUKUM MEN DELLE ‘IDHA EHTEDEJTUM ‘ILA ELLAHI MERXHI’UKUM XHEMI’ÆN FEJUNEBBI’UKUM BIMA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  5,106,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU SHEHADETU BEJNIKUM ‘IDHA HEDERE ‘EHEDEKUMUL-MEWTU HINEL-WESIJETI ETHNANI DHEWA ‘ADLIN MINKUM ‘EW ‘AHARANI MIN GAJRIKUM ‘IN ‘ENTUM DEREBTUM FIL-’ERDI FE’ESABETKUM MUSIBETUL-MEWTI TEHBISUNEHUMA MIN BA’DI ES-SELÆTI FEJUKSIMANI BILL
  5,107,FE’IN ‘UTHIRE ‘ALA ‘ENNEHUMA ESTEHEKKA ‘ITHMÆN FE’AHARANI JEKUMANI MEKAMEHUMA MINEL-LEDHINE ESTEHEKKA ‘ALEJHIMUL-’EWLEJANI FEJUKSIMANI BILLAHI LESHEHADETUNA ‘EHEKKU MIN SHEHADETIHIMA WE MA A’TEDEJNA ‘INNA ‘IDHÆN LEMINE EDH-DHALIMINE
  5,108,DHALIKE ‘EDNA ‘EN JE’TU BISH-SHEHADETI ‘ALA WEXHHIHA ‘EW JEHAFU ‘EN TUREDDE ‘EJMANUN BA’DE ‘EJMANIHIM WE ETTEKU ELLAHE WE ESMA’U WEL-LAHU LA JEHDIL-KAWMEL-FASIKINE
  5,109,JEWME JEXHMA’U ELLAHU ER-RUSULE FEJEKULU MADHA ‘UXHIBTUM KALU LA ‘ILME LENA ‘INNEKE ‘ENTE ‘ALLAMUL-GUJUBI
  5,110,‘IDH KALEL-LAHU JA ‘ISA EBNE MERJEME EDHKUR NI’METI ‘ALEJKE WE ‘ALA WE E-DETIKE ‘IDH ‘EJJEDTTUKE BIRUHIL-KUDUSI TUKELLIMU EN-NASE FIL-MEHDI WE KEHLÆN WE ‘IDH ‘ALLEMTUKEL-KITABE WEL-HIKMETE WET-TEWRÆTE WEL-’INXHILE WE ‘IDH TEHLUKU MINET-TINI KEHEJ’ETIT-TEJ
  5,111,WE ‘IDH ‘EWHEJTU ‘ILAL-HEWARIJINE ‘EN ‘AMINU BI WE BIRESULI KALU ‘AMENNA WE ESH/HED BI’ENNENA MUSLIMUNE
  5,112,‘IDH KALEL-HEWARIJUNE JA ‘ISA EBNE MERJEME HEL JESTETI’U REBBUKE ‘EN JUNEZZILE ‘ALEJNA MA’IDETEN MINE ES-SEMA’I KALE ETTEKU ELLAHE ‘IN KUNTUM MU’UMININE
  5,113,KALU NURIDU ‘EN NE’KULE MINHA WE TETME’INNE KULUBUNA WE NA’LEME ‘EN KAD SEDEKTENA WE NEKUNE ‘ALEJHA MINE ESH-SHAHIDINE
  5,114,KALE ‘ISA EBNU MERJEMEL-LEHUMME REBBENA ‘ENZIL ‘ALEJNA MA’IDETEN MINE ES-SEMA’I TEKUNU LENA ‘IDÆN LI’WWELINA WE ‘AHIRINA WE ‘AJETEN MINKE WE ERZUKNA WE ‘ENTE HAJRU ER-RAZIKINE
  5,115,KALEL-LAHU ‘INNI MUNEZZILUHA ‘ALEJKUM FEMEN JEKFUR BA’DU MINKUM FE’INNI ‘U’ADHDHIBUHU ‘ADHABÆN LA ‘U’ADHDHIBUHU ‘EHEDÆN MINEL-’ALEMINE
  5,116,WE ‘IDH KALEL-LAHU JA ‘ISA EBNE MERJEME ‘E’ENTE KULTE LILNNASI ETTEHIDHUNI WE ‘UMMIJE ‘ILEHEJNI MIN DUNI ELLAHI KALE SUBHANEKE MA JEKUNU LI ‘EN ‘EKULE MA LEJSE LI BIHEKKIN ‘IN KUNTU KULTUHU FEKAD ‘ALIMTEHU TA’LEMU MA FI NEFSI WE LA ‘A’LEMU MA FI NEFSIKE ‘
  5,117,MA KULTU LEHUM ‘ILLA MA ‘EMERTENI BIHI ‘ENI A’BUDU ELLAHE RABBI WE REBBEKUM WE KUNTU ‘ALEJHIM SHEHIDÆN MA DUMTU FIHIM FELEMMA TEWEFFEJTENI KUNTE ‘ENTE ER-REKIBE ‘ALEJHIM WE ‘ENTE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN SHEHIDUN
  5,118,‘IN TU’ADHDHIBHUM FE’INNEHUM ‘IBADUKE WE ‘IN TEGFIR LEHUM FE’INNEKE ‘ENTEL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  5,119,KALEL-LAHU HADHA JEWMU JENFA’U ES-SADIKINE SIDKUHUM LEHUM XHENNATUN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU HALIDINE FIHA ‘EBEDÆN REDIJEL-LAHU ‘ANHUM WE REDU ‘ANHU DHALIKEL-FEWZUL-’ADHIMU
  5,120,LILLAHI MULKU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MA FIHINNE WE HUWE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  6,1,EL-HEMDU LILLAHIL-LEDHI HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE WE XHE’ALE EDH-DHULUMATI WE EN-NURE THUMMEL-LEDHINE KEFERU BIREBBIHIM JA’DILUNE
  6,2,HUWEL-LEDHI HALEKAKUM MIN TININ THUMME KADA ‘EXHELÆN WE ‘EXHELUN MUSEMMEN ‘INDEHU THUMME ‘ENTUM TEMTERUNE
  6,3,WE HUWEL-LAHU FI ES-SEMAWATI WE FIL-’ERDI JA’LEMU SIRREKUM WE XHEHREKUM WE JA’LEMU MA TEKSIBUNE
  6,4,WE MA TE’TIHIM MIN ‘AJETIN MIN ‘AJATI RABBIHIM ‘ILLA KANU ‘ANHA MU’RIDINE
  6,5,FEKAD KEDHDHEBU BIL-HEKKI LEMMA XHA’EHUM FESEWFE JE’TIHIM ‘ENBA’U MA KANU BIHI JESTEHZI’UN
  6,6,‘ELEM JEREW KEM ‘EHLEKNA MIN KABLIHIM MIN KARNIN MEKKENNAHUM FIL-’ERDI MA LEM NUMEKKIN LEKUM WE ‘ERSELNA ES-SEMA’E ‘ALEJHIM MIDRARÆN WE XHE’ALNAL-’ENHARE TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHIM FE’EHLEKNAHUM BIDHUNUBIHIM WE ‘ENSHE’NA MIN BA’DIHIM KARNÆN ‘AHARINE
  6,7,WE LEW NEZZELNA ‘ALEJKE KITABÆN FI KIRTASIN FELEMESUHU BI’EJDIHIM LEKALEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘IN HADHA ‘ILLA SIHRUN MUBINUN
  6,8,WE KALU LEWLA ‘UNZILE ‘ALEJHI MELEKUN WE LEW ‘ENZELNA MELEKÆN LEKUDIJEL-’EMRU THUMME LA JUNDHERUNE
  6,9,WE LEW XHE’ALNAHU MELEKÆN LEXHE’ALNAHU REXHULÆN WE LELEBESNA ‘ALEJHIM MA JELBISUNE
  6,10,WE LEKADI ESTUHZI’E BIRUSULIN MIN KABLIKE FEHAKA BIEL-LEDHINE SEHIRU MINHUM MA KANU BIHI JESTEHZI’UN
  6,11,KUL SIRU FIL-’ERDI THUMME ENDHURU KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETUL-MUKEDHDHIBINE
  6,12,KUL LIMEN MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI KUL LILLAHI KETEBE ‘ALA NEFSIHI ER-REHMETE LEJEXHME’ANNEKUM ‘ILA JEWMIL-KIJAMETI LA REJBE FIHIL-LEDHINE HASIRU ‘ENFUSEHUM FEHUM LA JU’UMINUNE
  6,13,WE LEHU MA SEKENE FIL-LEJLI WE EN-NEHARI WE HUWE ES-SEMI’UL-’ALIMU
  6,14,KUL ‘EGAJREL-LAHI ‘ETTEHIDHU WELIJÆN FATIRI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE HUWE JUT’IMU WE LA JUT’AMU KUL ‘INNI ‘UMIRTU ‘EN ‘EKUNE ‘EWWELE MEN ‘ESLEME WE LA TEKUNENNE MINEL-MUSHRIKINE
  6,15,KUL ‘INNI ‘EHAFU ‘IN ‘ASEJTU RABBI ‘ADHABE JEWMIN ‘ADHIMIN
  6,16,MEN JUSREF ‘ANHU JEWME’IDHIN FEKAD REHIMEHU WE DHELIKEL-FEWZUL-MUBINU
  6,17,WE ‘IN JEMSESKEL-LAHU BIDURRIN FELA KASHIFE LEHU ‘ILLA HUWE WE ‘IN JEMSESKE BIHAJRIN FEHUWE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  6,18,WE HUWEL-KAHIRU FEWKA ‘IBADIHI WE HUWEL-HEKIMUL-HABIRU
  6,19,KUL ‘EJJU SHEJ’IN ‘EKBERU SHEHADETEN KULI ELLAHU SHEHIDUN BEJNI WE BEJNEKUM WE ‘UHIJE ‘ILEJJE HADHAL-KUR’ANU LI’NDHIREKUM BIHI WE MEN BELEGA ‘E’INNEKUM LETESH/HEDUNE ‘ENNE ME’A ELLAHI ‘ALIHETEN ‘UHRA KUL LA ‘ESH/HEDU KUL ‘INNEMA HUWE ‘ILEHUN WAHIDUN WE ‘I
  6,20,EL-LEDHINE ‘ATEJNAHUMUL-KITABE JA’RIFUNEHU KEMA JA’RIFUNE ‘EBNA’EHUMUL-LEDHINE HASIRU ‘ENFUSEHUM FEHUM LA JU’UMINUNE
  6,21,WE MEN ‘EDHLEMU MIMMENI EFTERA ‘ALA ELLAHI KEDHIBÆN ‘EW KEDHDHEBE BI’AJATIHI ‘INNEHU LA JUFLIHU EDH-DHALIMUNE
  6,22,WE JEWME NEHSHURUHUM XHEMI’ÆN THUMME NEKULU LILLEDHINE ‘ESHREKU ‘EJNE SHUREKA’UUKUMUL-LEDHINE KUNTUM TEZ’UMUNE
  6,23,THUMME LEM TEKUN FITNETUHUM ‘ILLA ‘EN KALU WEL-LEHI RABBINA MA KUNNA MUSHRIKINE
  6,24,ENDHUR KEJFE KEDHEBU ‘ALA ‘ENFUSIHIM WE DELLE ‘ANHUM MA KANU JEFTERUNE
  6,25,WE MINHUM MEN JESTEMI’U ‘ILEJKE WE XHE’ALNA ‘ALA KULUBIHIM ‘EKINNETEN ‘EN JEFKAHUHU WE FI ‘ADHANIHIM WEKRÆN WE ‘IN JEREW KULLE ‘AJETIN LA JU’UMINU BIHA HETTA ‘IDHA XHA’UKE JUXHADILUNEKE JEKULUL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘IN HADHA ‘ILLA ‘ESATIRUL-’EWWELINE
  6,26,WE HUM JENHEWNE ‘ANHU WE JEN’EWNE ‘ANHU WE ‘IN JUHLIKUNE ‘ILLA ‘ENFUSEHUM WE MA JESH’URUNE
  6,27,WE LEW TERA ‘IDH WUKIFU ‘ALA EN-NARI FEKALU JA LEJTENA NUREDDU WE LA NUKEDHDHIBE BI’AJATI RABBINA WE NEKUNE MINEL-MU’UMININE
  6,28,BEL BEDA LEHUM MA KANU JUHFUNE MIN KABLU WE LEW RUDDU LA’ADU LIMA NUHU ‘ANHU WE ‘INNEHUM LEKADHIBUNE
  6,29,WE KALU ‘IN HIJE ‘ILLA HEJATUNA ED-DUNJA WE MA NEHNU BIMEB’UTHINE
  6,30,WE LEW TERA ‘IDH WUKIFU ‘ALA RABBIHIM KALE ‘ELEJSE HADHA BIL-HEKKI KALU BELA WE RABBINA KALE FEDHUKUL-’ADHABE BIMA KUNTUM TEKFURUNE
  6,31,KAD HASIREL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BILIKA’I ELLAHI HETTA ‘IDHA XHA’ET/HUMU ES-SA’ATU BEGTETEN KALU JA HESRETENA ‘ALA MA FERRETNA FIHA WE HUM JEHMILUNE ‘EWZAREHUM ‘ALA DHUHURIHIM ‘ELA SA’E MA JEZIRUNE
  6,32,WE MAL-HEJÆTU ED-DUNJA ‘ILLA LA’IBUN WE LEHWUN WE LELDDARUL-’AHIRETU HAJRUN LILLEDHINE JETTEKUNE ‘EFELA TA’KILUNE
  6,33,KAD NA’LEMU ‘INNEHU LEJEHZUNUKEL-LEDHI JEKULUNE FE’INNEHUM LA JUKEDHDHIBUNEKE WE LEKINNE EDH-DHALIMINE BI’AJATI ELLAHI JEXHHEDUNE
  6,34,WE LEKAD KUDHDHIBET RUSULUN MIN KABLIKE FESEBERU ‘ALA MA KUDHDHIBU WE ‘UDHU HETTA ‘ETAHUM NESRUNA WE LA MUBEDDILE LIKELIMATI ELLAHI WE LEKAD XHA’EKE MIN NEBE’IL-MURSELINE
  6,35,WE ‘IN KANE KEBURE ‘ALEJKE ‘I’RADUHUM FE’INI ESTETA’TE ‘EN TEBTEGIJE NEFEKÆN FIL-’ERDI ‘EW SULLEMÆN FI ES-SEMA’I FETE’TIJEHUM BI’AJETIN WE LEW SHA’EL-LAHU LEXHEME’AHUM ‘ALEL-HUDA FELA TEKUNENNE MINEL-XHAHILINE
  6,36,‘INNEMA JESTEXHIBUL-LEDHINE JESMA’UNE WEL-MEWTA JEB’ATHUHUMU ELLAHU THUMME ‘ILEJHI JURXHA’UNE
  6,37,WE KALU LEWLA NUZZILE ‘ALEJHI ‘AJETUN MIN RABBIHI KUL ‘INNALL-LLAHE KADIRUN ‘ALA ‘EN JUNEZZILE ‘AJETEN WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHEREHUM LA JA’LEMUNE
  6,38,WE MA MIN DABBETIN FIL-’ERDI WE LA TA’IRIN JETIRU BIXHENAHEJHI ‘ILLA ‘UMEMUN ‘EMTHALUKUM MA FERRETNA FIL-KITABI MIN SHEJ’IN THUMME ‘ILA RABBIHIM JUHSHERUNE
  6,39,WEL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA SUMMUN WE BUKMUN FI EDH-DHULUMATI MEN JESHE’I ELLAHU JUDLILHU WE MEN JESHE’ JEXH’ALHU ‘ALA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  6,40,KUL ‘ERE’EJTEKUM ‘IN ‘ETAKUM ‘ADHABU ELLAHI ‘EW ‘ETETKUMU ES-SA’ATU ‘EGAJREL-LAHI TED’UNE ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  6,41,BEL ‘IJAHU TED’UNE FEJEKSHIFU MA TED’UNE ‘ILEJHI ‘IN SHA’E WE TENSEWNE MA TUSHRIKUNE
  6,42,WE LEKAD ‘ERSELNA ‘ILA ‘UMEMIN MIN KABLIKE FE’EHADHNAHUM BIL-BE’SA’I WE ED-DERRA’I LE’ALLEHUM JETEDERRA’UNE
  6,43,FELEWLA ‘IDH XHA’EHUM BE’SUNA TEDERRA’U WE LEKIN KASET KULUBUHUM WE ZEJJENE LEHUMU ESH-SHEJTANU MA KANU JA’MELUN
  6,44,FELEMMA NESU MA DHUKKIRU BIHI FETEHNA ‘ALEJHIM ‘EBWABE KULLI SHEJ’IN HETTA ‘IDHA FERIHU BIMA ‘UTU ‘EHADHNAHUM BEGTETEN FE’IDHA HUM MUBLISUNE
  6,45,FEKUTI’A DABIRUL-KAWMIL-LEDHINE DHELEMU WEL-HEMDU LILLAHI RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  6,46,KUL ‘ERE’EJTUM ‘IN ‘EHADHEL-LAHU SEM’AKUM WE ‘EBSAREKUM WE HATEME ‘ALA KULUBIKUM MEN ‘ILEHUN GAJRU ELLAHI JE’TIKUM BIHI ENDHUR KEJFE NUSERRIFUL-’AJATI THUMME HUM JESDIFUNE
  6,47,KUL ‘ERE’EJTEKUM ‘IN ‘ETAKUM ‘ADHABU ELLAHI BEGTETEN ‘EW XHEHRETEN HEL JUHLEKU ‘ILLAL-KAWMU EDH-DHALIMUNE
  6,48,WE MA NURSILUL-MURSELINE ‘ILLA MUBESHSHIRINE WE MUNDHIRINE FEMEN ‘AMENE WE ‘ESLEHE FELA HAWFUN ‘ALEJHIM WE LA HUM JEHZENUNE
  6,49,WEL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA JEMESSUHUMUL-’ADHABU BIMA KANU JEFSUKUNE
  6,50,KUL LA ‘EKULU LEKUM ‘INDI HAZA’INU ELLAHI WE LA ‘A’LEMUL-GAJBE WE LA ‘EKULU LEKUM ‘INNI MELEKUN ‘IN ‘ETTEBI’U ‘ILLA MA JUHA ‘ILEJJE KUL HEL JESTEWIL-’A’MA WEL-BESIRU ‘EFELA TETEFEKKERUNE
  6,51,WE ‘ENDHIR BIHIL-LEDHINE JEHAFUNE ‘EN JUHSHERU ‘ILA RABBIHIM LEJSE LEHUM MIN DUNIHI WE LIJUN WE LA SHEFI’UN LE’ALLEHUM JETTEKUNE
  6,52,WE LA TETRUDIL-LEDHINE JED’UNE REBBEHUM BIL-GADÆTI WEL-’ASHIJI JURIDUNE WEXHHEHU MA ‘ALEJKE MIN HISABIHIM MIN SHEJ’IN WE MA MIN HISABIKE ‘ALEJHIM MIN SHEJ’IN FETETRUDEHUM FETEKUNE MINE EDH-DHALIMINE
  6,53,WE KEDHELIKE FETENNA BA’DEHUM BIBA’DIN LIJEKULU ‘EHA’UULA’ MENNEL-LAHU ‘ALEJHIM MIN BEJNINA ‘ELEJSEL-LAHU BI’A’LEME BISH-SHAKIRINE
  6,54,WE ‘IDHA XHA’EKEL-LEDHINE JU’UMINUNE BI’AJATINA FEKUL SELAMUN ‘ALEJKUM KETEBE REBBUKUM ‘ALA NEFSIHI ER-REHMETE ‘ENNEHU MEN ‘AMILE MINKUM SU’ÆN BIXHEHALETIN THUMME TABE MIN BA’DIHI WE ‘ESLEHE FE’ENNEHU GAFURUN REHIMUN
  6,55,WE KEDHELIKE NUFESSILUL-’AJATI WE LITESTEBINE SEBILUL-MUXHRIMINE
  6,56,KUL ‘INNI NUHITU ‘EN ‘A’BUDEL-LEDHINE TED’UNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI KUL LA ‘ETTEBI’U ‘EHWA’EKUM KAD DELELTU ‘IDHÆN WE MA ‘ENA MINEL-MUHTEDINE
  6,57,KUL ‘INNI ‘ALA BEJJINETIN MIN RABBI WE KEDHDHEBTUM BIHI MA ‘INDI MA TESTA’XHILUNE BIHI ‘INIL-HUKMU ‘ILLA LILLAHI JEKUSSUL-HEKKA WE HUWE HAJRUL-FASILINE
  6,58,KUL LEW ‘ENNE ‘INDI MA TESTA’XHILUNE BIHI LEKUDIJEL-’EMRU BEJNI WE BEJNEKUM WEL-LAHU ‘A’LEMU BIDH-DHALIMINE
  6,59,WE ‘INDEHU MEFATIHUL-GAJBI LA JA’LEMUHA ‘ILLA HUWE WE JA’LEMU MA FIL-BERRI WEL-BEHRI WE MA TESKUTU MIN WEREKATIN ‘ILLA JA’LEMUHA WE LA HEBBETIN FI DHULUMATIL-’ERDI WE LA RETBIN WE LA JA BISIN ‘ILLA FI KITABIN MUBININ
  6,60,WE HUWEL-LEDHI JETEWEFFAKUM BIL-LEJLI WE JA’LEMU MA XHEREHTUM BIN-NEHARI THUMME JEB’ATHUKUM FIHI LIJUKDA ‘EXHELUN MUSEMMEN THUMME ‘ILEJHI MERXHI’UKUM THUMME JUNEBBI’UKUM BIMA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  6,61,WE HUWEL-KAHIRU FEWKA ‘IBADIHI WE JURSILU ‘ALEJKUM HEFEDHETEN HETTA ‘IDHA XHA’E ‘EHEDEKUMUL-MEWTU TEWEFFET/HU RUSULUNA WE HUM LA JUFERRITUNE
  6,62,THUMME RUDDU ‘ILA ELLAHI MEWLAHUMUL-HEKKI ‘ELA LEHUL-HUKMU WE HUWE ‘ESRA’UL-HASIBINE
  6,63,KUL MEN JUNEXHXHIKUM MIN DHULUMATIL-BERRI WEL-BEHRI TED’UNEHU TEDERRU’ÆN WE HUFJETEN LE’IN ‘ENXHANA MIN HEDHIHI LENEKUNENNE MINE ESH-SHAKIRINE
  6,64,KULI ELLAHU JUNEXHXHIKUM MINHA WE MIN KULLI KERBIN THUMME ‘ENTUM TUSHRIKUNE
  6,65,KUL HUWEL-KADIRU ‘ALA ‘EN JEB’ATHE ‘ALEJKUM ‘ADHABÆN MIN FEWKIKUM ‘EW MIN TEHTI ‘ERXHULIKUM ‘EW JELBISEKUM SHIJA’ÆN WE JUDHIKA BA’DEKUM BE’SE BA’DIN ENDHUR KEJFE NUSERRIFUL-’AJATI LE’ALLEHUM JEFKAHUNE
  6,66,WE KEDHDHEBE BIHI KAWMUKE WE HUWEL-HEKKU KUL LESTU ‘ALEJKUM BIWEKILIN
  6,67,LIKULLI NEBE’IIN MUSTEKARRUN WE SEWFE TA’LEMUNE
  6,68,WE ‘IDHA RE’EJTEL-LEDHINE JEHUDUNE FI ‘AJATINA FE’A’RID ‘ANHUM HETTA JEHUDU FI HEDITHIN GAJRIHI WE ‘IMMA JUNSIJENNEKE ESH-SHEJTANU FELA TEK’UD BA’DE EDH-DHIKRA ME’AL-KAWMI EDH-DHALIMINE
  6,69,WE MA ‘ALEL-LEDHINE JETTEKUNE MIN HISABIHIM MIN SHEJ’IN WE LEKIN DHIKRA LE’ALLEHUM JETTEKUNE
  6,70,WE DHERIL-LEDHINE ETTEHADHU DINEHUM LA’IBÆN WE LEHWEN WE GARRET/HUMUL-HEJÆTU ED-DUNJA WE DHEKKIR BIHI ‘EN TUBSELE NEFSUN BIMA KESEBET LEJSE LEHA MIN DUNI ELLAHI WE LIJUN WE LA SHEFI’UN WE ‘IN TA’DIL KULLE ‘ADLIN LA JU’UHADH MINHA ‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE ‘UBSILU
  6,71,KUL ‘ENED’U MIN DUNI ELLAHI MA LA JENFA’UNA WE LA JEDURRUNA WE NUREDDU ‘ALA ‘A’KABINA BA’DE ‘IDH HEDANALLAHU KALLEDHI ESTEHWET/HU ESH-SHEJATINU FIL-’ERDI HEJRANE LEHU ‘ESHABUN JED’UNEHU ‘ILAL-HUDA E’TINA KUL ‘INNE HUDA ELLAHI HUWEL-HUDA WE ‘UMIRNA LINUSLI
  6,72,WE ‘EN ‘EKIMU ES-SELÆTE WE ETTEKUHU WE HUWEL-LEDHI ‘ILEJHI TUHSHERUNE
  6,73,WE HUWEL-LEDHI HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE BIL-HEKKI WE JEWME JEKULU KUN FEJEKUNU KAWLUHUL-HEKKU WE LEHUL-MULKU JEWME JUNFEHU FI ES-SURI ‘ALIMUL-GAJBI WE ESH-SHEHADETI WE HUWEL-HEKIMUL-HABIR
  6,74,WE ‘IDH KALE ‘IBRAHIMU LI’EBIHI ‘AZERE ‘ETETTEHIDHU ‘ESNAMÆN ‘ALIHETEN ‘INNI ‘ERAKE WE KAWMEKE FI DELALIN MUBININ
  6,75,WE KEDHELIKE NURI ‘IBRAHIME MELEKUTE ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE LIJEKUNE MINEL-MUKININE
  6,76,FELEMMA XHENNE ‘ALEJHIL-LEJLU RE’A KEWKEBÆN KALE HADHA RABBI FELEMMA ‘EFELE KALE LA ‘UHIBBUL-’AFILINE
  6,77,FELEMMA RE’AL-KAMERE BAZIGÆN KALE HADHA RABBI FELEMMA ‘EFELE KALE LE’IN LEM JEHDINI RABBI LE’EKUNENNE MINEL-KAWMI ED-DALLINE
  6,78,FELEMMA RE’A ESH-SHEMSE BAZIGATEN KALE HADHA RABBI HADHA ‘EKBERU FELEMMA ‘EFELET KALE JA KAWMI ‘INNI BERI’UN MIMMA TUSHRIKUNE
  6,79,‘INNI WEXHXHEHTU WEXHHIJE LILLEDHI FETERE ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE HENIFÆN WE MA ‘ENA MINEL-MUSHRIKINE
  6,80,WE HAXHXHEHU KAWMUHU KALE ‘ETUHAXHXHUNI FI ELLAHI WE KAD HEDANI WE LA ‘EHAFU MA TUSHRIKUNE BIHI ‘ILLA ‘EN JESHA’E RABBI SHEJ’ÆN WESI’A RABBI KULLE SHEJ’IN ‘ILMÆN ‘EFELA TETEDHEKKERUNE
  6,81,WE KEJFE ‘EHAFU MA ‘ESHREKTUM WE LA TEHAFUNE ‘ENNEKUM ‘ESHREKTUM BILLAHI MA LEM JUNEZZIL BIHI ‘ALEJKUM SULTANÆN FE’EJJUL-FERIKAJNI ‘EHEKKU BIL-’EMNI ‘IN KUNTUM TA’LEMUNE
  6,82,EL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE LEM JELBISU ‘IMANEHUM BIDHULMIN ‘ULA’IKE LEHUMUL-’EMNU WE HUM MUHTEDUNE
  6,83,WE TILKE HUXHXHETUNA ‘ATEJNAHA ‘IBRAHIME ‘ALA KAWMIHI NERFA’U DEREXHATIN MEN NESHA’U ‘INNE REBBEKE HEKIMUN ‘ALIMUN
  6,84,WE WEHEBNA LEHU ‘ISHAKA WE JA’KUBE KULLÆN HEDEJNA WE NUHÆN HEDEJNA MIN KABLU WE MIN DHURRIJETIHI DAWUDE WE SULEJMANE WE ‘EJJUBE WE JUSUFE WE MUSA WE HARUNE WE KEDHELIKE NEXHZIL-MUHSININE
  6,85,WE ZEKERIJA WE JEHJA WE ‘ISA WE ‘ILJASE KULLUN MINE ES-SALIHINE
  6,86,WE ‘ISMA’ILE WEL-JESE’A WE JUNUS WE LUTÆN WE KULLÆN FEDDELNA ‘ALEL-’ALEMINE
  6,87,WE MIN ‘ABA’IHIM WE DHURRIJATIHIM WE ‘IHWANIHIM WE EXHTEBEJNAHUM WE HEDEJNAHUM ‘ILA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  6,88,DHALIKE HUDA ELLAHI JEHDI BIHI MEN JESHA’U MIN ‘IBADIHI WE LEW ‘ESHREKU LEHEBITE ‘ANHUM MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  6,89,‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE ‘ATEJNAHUMUL-KITABE WEL-HUKME WE EN-NUBUWETE FE’IN JEKFUR BIHA HA’UULA’ FEKAD WE KKELNA BIHA KAWMÆN LEJSU BIHA BIKAFIRINE
  6,90,‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE HEDALLAHU FEBIHUDAHUMU EKTEDIHI KUL LA ‘ES’ELUKUM ‘ALEJHI ‘EXHRÆN ‘IN HUWE ‘ILLA DHIKRA LIL’ALEMINE
  6,91,WE MA KADERU ELLAHE HEKKA KADRIHI ‘IDH KALU MA ‘ENZELEL-LAHU ‘ALA BESHERIN MIN SHEJ’IN KUL MEN ‘ENZELEL-KITABEL-LEDHI XHA’E BIHI MUSA NURÆN WE HUDEN LILNNASI TEXH’ALUNEHU KARATISE TUBDUNEHA WE TUHFUNE KETHIRÆN WE ‘ULLIMTUM MA LEM TA’LEMU ‘ENTUM WE LA ‘ABA
  6,92,WE HEDHA KITABUN ‘ENZELNAHU MUBAREKUN MUSEDDIKUL-LEDHI BEJNE JEDEJHI WE LITUNDHIRE ‘UMMEL-KURA WE MEN HEWLEHA WEL-LEDHINE JU’UMINUNE BIL-’AHIRETI JU’UMINUNE BIHI WE HUM ‘ALA SELATIHIM JUHAFIDHUNE
  6,93,WE MEN ‘EDHLEMU MIMMENI EFTERA ‘ALA ELLAHI KEDHIBÆN ‘EW KALE ‘UHIJE ‘ILEJJE WE LEM JUHE ‘ILEJHI SHEJ’UN WE MEN KALE SE’UNZILU MITHLE MA ‘ENZELEL-LAHU WE LEW TERA ‘IDHI EDH-DHALIMUNE FI GAMERATIL-MEWTI WEL-MELA’IKETU BASITU ‘EJDIHIM ‘EHRIXHU ‘ENFUSEKUMUL-J
  6,94,WE LEKAD XHI’TUMUNA FURADA KEMA HALEKNAKUM ‘EWWELE MERRETIN WE TEREKTUM MA HAWWELNAKUM WERA’E DHUHURIKUM WE MA NERA ME’AKUM SHUFA’A’EKUMUL-LEDHINE ZE’AMTUM ‘ENNEHUM FIKUM SHUREKA’U LEKAD TEKATTE’A BEJNEKUM WE DELLE ‘ANKUM MA KUNTUM TEZ’UMUNE
  6,95,‘INNALL-LLAHE FALIKUL-HEBBI WE EN-NEWA JUHRIXHUL-HEJJE MINEL-MEJJITI WE MUHRIXHUL-MEJJITI MINEL-HEJJI DHELIKUMU ELLAHU FE’ENNA TU’UFEKUNE
  6,96,FALIKUL-’ISBAHI WE XHE’ALEL-LEJLE SEKENÆN WE ESH-SHEMSE WEL-KAMERE HUSBANÆN DHALIKE TEKDIRUL-’AZIZIL-’ALIMI
  6,97,WE HUWEL-LEDHI XHE’ALE LEKUMU EN-NUXHUME LITEHTEDU BIHA FI DHULUMATIL-BERRI WEL-BEHRI KAD FESSELNAL-’AJATI LIKAWMIN JA’LEMUNE
  6,98,WE HUWEL-LEDHI ‘ENSHE’EKUM MIN NEFSIN WAHIDETIN FEMUSTEKARRUN WE MUSTEWDA’UN KAD FESSELNAL-’AJATI LIKAWMIN JEFKAHUN
  6,99,WE HUWEL-LEDHI ‘ENZELE MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN FE’EHREXHNA BIHI NEBATE KULLI SHEJ’IN FE’EHREXHNA MINHU HADIRÆN NUHRIXHU MINHU HEBBÆN MUTERAKIBÆN WE MINE EN-NEHLI MIN TEL’IHA KINWANUN DANIJETUN WE XHENNATIN MIN ‘A’NABIN WE EZ-ZEJTUNE WE ER-RUMMANE MUSHTEBIHÆN
  6,100,WE XHE’ALU LILLAHI SHUREKA’EL-XHINNE WE HALEKAHUM WE HAREKU LEHU BENINE WE BENATIN BIGAJRI ‘ILMIN SUBHANEHU WE TA’ALA ‘AMMA JESIFUNE
  6,101,BEDI’U ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI ‘ENNA JEKUNU LEHU WELEDUN WE LEM TEKUN LEHU SAHIBETUN WE HALEKA KULLE SHEJ’IN WE HUWE BIKULLI SHEJ’IN ‘ALIMUN
  6,102,DHELIKUMU ELLAHU REBBUKUM LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE HALIKU KULLI SHEJ’IN FA’BUDUHU WE HUWE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN WE KILUN
  6,103,LA TUDRIKUHUL-’EBSARU WE HUWE JUDRIKUL-’EBSARE WE HUWEL-LETIFUL-HABIR
  6,104,KAD XHA’EKUM BESA’IRU MIN RABBIKUM FEMEN ‘EBSERE FELINEFSIHI WE MEN ‘AMIJE FE’ALEJHA WE MA ‘ENA ‘ALEJKUM BIHEFIDHIN
  6,105,WE KEDHELIKE NUSERRIFUL-’AJATI WE LIJEKULU DERESTE WE LINUBEJJINEHU LIKAWMIN JA’LEMUNE
  6,106,ETTEBI’ MA ‘UHIJE ‘ILEJKE MIN RABBIKE LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE WE ‘A’RID ‘ANIL-MUSHRIKINE
  6,107,WE LEW SHA’EL-LAHU MA ‘ESHREKU WE MA XHE’ALNAKE ‘ALEJHIM HEFIDHÆN WE MA ‘ENTE ‘ALEJHIM BIWEKILIN
  6,108,WE LA TESUBBUL-LEDHINE JED’UNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI FEJESUBBU ELLAHE ‘ADWEN BIGAJRI ‘ILMIN KEDHALIKE ZEJJENNA LIKULLI ‘UMMETIN ‘AMELEHUM THUMME ‘ILA RABBIHIM MERXHI’UHUM FEJUNEBBI’UHUM BIMA KANU JA’MELUNE
  6,109,WE ‘EKSEMU BILLAHI XHEHDE ‘EJMANIHIM LE’IN XHA’ET/HUM ‘AJETUN LEJU’UMINUNNE BIHA KUL ‘INNEMAL-’AJATU ‘INDEL-LAHI WE MA JUSH’IRUKUM ‘ENNEHA ‘IDHA XHA’ET LA JU’UMINUNE
  6,110,WE NUKALLIBU ‘EF’IDETEHUM WE ‘EBSAREHUM KEMA LEM JU’UMINU BIHI ‘EWWELE MERRETIN WE NEDHERUHUM FI TUGJANIHIM JA’MEHUNE